  "body": "**NOTE:** _**there is significant difference between ### SHARE and ### INVITE community flows on mobile**_\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n\r\n1. as a mobile (device A) -> create a community that requires approval to join\r\n2. as a mobile (device A) -> add desktop (device B) to contacts\r\n3. as mobile (device A) -> go to community you just created and tap + button -> invite people\r\n4. as mobile (device A) -> select desktop (device B) to send an invitation to join the community\r\n\r\n**As a result on device B (desktop):**\r\n\r\n- community invitation is appeared in 1x1 chat as joined\r\n- user is autojoined the community \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** user should bypass the accepting invitation flow (tap Join to confirm the will to join it). No auto join flow should be present. NOTE: since this is **invitation**  and not sharing -> no request access flow expected (this is working correctly).\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1431\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-05-06 at 19 35 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/117334521-c2bc7e00-aea2-11eb-8cb8-9de5a59b9b49.png\">\r\n",
